diplomats and politicians

00:01:30.670 --> 00:01:33.225
who were trying to
make the country.

00:01:33.225 --> 00:01:36.220
And so I was born on the
that soup of that change

00:01:36.220 --> 00:01:38.140
and this kind of old
world, new world trying

00:01:38.140 --> 00:01:40.000
to forge a new identity.

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.760
And my father was really part
of that generation of diplomats

00:01:42.760 --> 00:01:45.340
