Africa first, but then

00:01:45.340 --> 00:01:48.400
the world, to learn how to
be diplomats of a state.

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:51.850
And so my childhood was two
years in a different city,

00:01:51.850 --> 00:01:53.960
six months, three months.

00:01:53.960 --> 00:01:55.070
And we went from--

00:01:55.070 --> 00:01:57.250
my parents are [INAUDIBLE],,
with just west Africa,

00:01:57.250 --> 00:02:01.130
but me and my brothers
were born in east Africa,

00:02:01.130 --> 00:02:03.970
so Uganda, Kenya.

00:02:03.970 --> 00:02:08.050
