Africa, to the Middle East,

00:02:08.050 --> 00:02:09.460
and then to Europe.

00:02:09.460 --> 00:02:14.770
So by the time I was 13, I had
sort of lived in nearly 15,

00:02:14.770 --> 00:02:16.270
20 cities.

00:02:16.270 --> 00:02:18.460
SHIH HUA LIONG: And why
