00:31:35.250 --> 00:31:37.770
of these developments
elsewhere in the US,

00:31:37.770 --> 00:31:40.140
that would be interesting.

00:31:40.140 --> 00:31:42.750
DAVID ADJAYE: Two
great questions.

00:31:42.750 --> 00:31:44.580
I'll start with the
