00:33:16.080 --> 00:33:18.600
When you're working on these
incredibly complex projects

00:33:18.600 --> 00:33:22.020
where you're working
with the government,

00:33:22.020 --> 00:33:24.270
the local authority,
community stakeholder groups,

00:33:24.270 --> 00:33:26.100
what we've decided
