to buy homes in places where--

00:44:47.350 --> 00:44:51.690
so it's a very kind
of complicated dynamic

00:44:51.690 --> 00:44:53.100
that actually does good.

00:44:53.100 --> 00:44:56.100
It does some harm because it
changes these communities.

00:44:56.100 --> 00:44:59.520
